<br>
She found her seat and sat down. Her eyes drifting around the room,stopping on Zelia. She stared at her for a long moment,then looked away. Saddened and Angered by the whole situation. That was her granddaughter sitting in the center of the room,and this was acctually the first time she had seen her since Zelia was just a baby. Can't help but feel she could have done something for her long ago,but now it was far too late.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonqueenyakut.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>  Posts: 62<br> <font color=#993300>(1/25/02 4:55:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=332.topic&index=30>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Gabby</span><hr size=1> Yakut smiled as Gabrielle walked onto the scene. Gabrielle had helped Yakut birth her second child Glory. She owed a debt to Gabrielle. As Zelia entered she gave a slight supporting smile to her. <p>§-:¦:-§ Yakut §-:¦:-§

Amazon Queen, Amazon Shamaness, and Amazon Mother...Your good old Northern Amazon!
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 297<br> <font color=#993300>(1/26/02 4:45:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=332.topic&index=31>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Chieftess Enters</span><hr size=1> Samsara had been recovering her memories of her life as Alysia. She had spoken with her daughter Belle and was learning more and more things of who she was now.<br>
<br>
At this time, she had fully mastered the new language and had learned through Aly's scrolls of her friends and family.<br>
<br>
Alysia entered the hut wearing her amazon leathers. She wore no boots and carried no weapons with her. Her short blonde hair was a bit damp from a recent dip in teh pond.<br>
<br>
She looked around as she spotted Hippolyte and Yakut. In the scrolls so far they were the only ones who she remembered.<br>
<br>
She walked up taking her place at the Cheiftess' Seat in the High Council. This was going to be a difficult trial. Alysia knew a great deal of forgiveness, but Samsara was harsh, and knew nothing of mercy.<br>
<br>
