</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenvaria.showPublicProfile?language=EN>QueenVaria</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://hometown.aol.com/cristalc15/images/tjcontenderpremiere.bmp" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 202<br> <font color=#993300>(1/26/02 8:55:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=332.topic&index=35>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/cristalc15/images/tsianina2.bmp WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: As everyone arrives</span><hr size=1> Varia crossed her arms across her chest and sank down in her chair, intending to remain invisible throughout the proceedings, only there to offer Zelia some comfort and love. She didn't want to see this, she didn't know how things were going to turn out. And uncertainty was not pleasant for Varia. <p><html> <font face="Signet Roundhand ATT" size="+1"> Varia Angelina Avande </font> </html></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonqueenyakut.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>  Posts: 65<br> <font color=#993300>(1/27/02 2:48:42 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=332.topic&index=36>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Shamanes Yakut.</span><hr size=1> Yakut watched as Alysia/Samsara entered and smiled. Yakut thought of Aly as family, Samsara or not. She was wondering if Raven or Lynn or Christanna was to show. Though they were not members of SoT, it would be nice if Hippolyte would let them sit and watch. Also Yakut thought she needed to see Belle more often. Yakut had to get the trial off her mind a bit 'til it began. So it was more waiting...... <p>§-:¦:-§ Yakut §-:¦:-§

Amazon Queen, Amazon Shamaness, and Amazon Mother...Your good old Northern Amazon!
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uchristannagoddessofpeace.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Christanna Goddess of Peace</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#993300>(1/27/02 3:11:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=332.topic&index=37>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/cristalc15/images/mariabello.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Shamaness Yakut.</span><hr size=1> Christanna could sense that Yakut needed her, so she showed up at the trial. She lingered outside the door, though, waiting to be told if she was allowed inside. <p><html> <center> <font face="lucida casual" size="+1"> ~ Tanna ~ </font> </center> </html></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uamazonqueenyakut.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amazon Queen Yakut </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>  Posts: 69<br> <font color=#993300>(1/27/02 6:46:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=332.topic&index=38>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/cristalc15/images/yakut.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Tanna</span><hr size=1> Yakut notice Tanna outsidde and smiled. She looked to Queen Hippolyte and bowed her lightly before she spoke.<br>
